        <h3 class="font-serif text-lg text-primary mb-3">From zero process to board-ready in 3 weeks</h3>
        <p class="text-text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">
          A Series B biotech was 6 weeks from their first board meeting with new investors. No prep process, no materials template, no action tracking system.
        </p>
        <div class="border-t border-primary/[0.06] pt-4">
          <p class="text-sm text-primary font-medium mb-1">What I built:</p>
          <p class="text-text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">Complete board prep system: materials timeline, template deck, committee briefing docs, pre-meeting packages, and post-meeting action tracker.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-4 bg-secondary/5 rounded-lg p-3">
          <p class="text-secondary text-sm font-semibold">Board materials delivered 5 business days early, every quarter. System still in use 18 months later.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Case Study 2 -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-primary/[0.06] p-7">
