        <h3 class="font-serif text-lg text-primary mb-3">New executives went from 90 days to hit stride to under 60</h3>
        <p class="text-text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">
          New leaders were spending their first month figuring out who to talk to, what meetings mattered, and how things actually worked. Knowledge lived in people's heads, not systems.
        </p>
        <div class="border-t border-primary/[0.06] pt-4">
          <p class="text-sm text-primary font-medium mb-1">What I built:</p>
          <p class="text-text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">90-day onboarding playbook: stakeholder map, meeting cadence guide, decision-rights matrix, and communication rhythm documentation.</p>
